# ACGS Code Owners - Documentation Review Requirements
# Constitutional Hash: cdd01ef066bc6cf2
#
# This file defines mandatory reviewers for different parts of the ACGS codebase
# to ensure proper documentation review and constitutional compliance.
#
# Format: path/pattern @reviewer1 @reviewer2
#
# Global fallback - requires at least one review for any change
* @acgs-maintainers

# Documentation - Requires documentation team review
docs/ @acgs-docs-team @acgs-platform-team
README.md @acgs-docs-team @acgs-platform-team

