# Team Definitions (GitHub teams should be created to match these)
#
# @acgs-maintainers - Core maintainers with overall repository access
# @acgs-docs-team - Documentation team responsible for content quality
# @acgs-platform-team - Platform engineering team
# @acgs-security-team - Security engineering team
# @acgs-devops-team - DevOps and infrastructure team
# @acgs-api-team - API design and integration team
# @acgs-service-owners - Service owners and developers
# @acgs-sre-team - Site reliability engineering team
# @acgs-operations-team - Operations and support team
# @acgs-architecture-team - Architecture and design team
# @acgs-compliance-team - Compliance and audit team
# @acgs-auth-team - Authentication service team
# @acgs-ai-team - Constitutional AI service team
# @acgs-integrity-team - Integrity service team
# @acgs-verification-team - Formal verification service team
# @acgs-governance-team - Governance synthesis service team
# @acgs-policy-team - Policy governance service team
# @acgs-evolution-team - Evolutionary computation service team
# @acgs-performance-team - Performance engineering team
# @acgs-qa-team - Quality assurance team
# @acgs-data-team - Data engineering team
# @acgs-legal-team - Legal and compliance team
# @acgs-product-team - Product management team

